snippet.title: Lies of P - Official Release Window Trailer | IGN Fan Fest 2023
snippet.description:
Lies of P is an action soulslike game set in a cruel, dark Belle Époque world where you play as Pinocchio. Lies of P is coming to PC, PS4, PS5, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and Game Pass in August 2023. 

Fan Fest is an event where fans from all over the world come together to celebrate their most anticipated movies, TV shows, and games. Streaming wherever you get IGN.

#IGN #Gaming
